{
  "stem": "20083.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did manage still to live in their huge apartment in the Kurfurstendamm, which is the Fifth Avenue of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- I do know, for instance, that they also has started to renting rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the people who they rented to was a woman by the name of Marika Roekk-- R-O-E-K-K, who happened to be a movie star.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she-- whenever I visited my father during the-- on weekends, she always had a boyfriend staying with her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That I remember, it impressed me enormously at that age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he also had one of the most famous horse-back riders staying with him, too, as what they call untermieter, a lodger.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they make-- made ends meet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they could still pay child support to my mother, who also let rooms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm quite sure there were some.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now if any Jewish organizations ever helped my mother, I simply never asked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just didn't occur to me as a youngster to say, does any Jewish organization support us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I do know that my father still paid child support to us and my mother still made a little bit of money from renting rooms.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I did not go into, at that age, into any further financial details.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Offhand, I have to be absolutely honest, offhand I can not remember a single incident where I saw any member of the SS or SA hitting or striking Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember during the Kristallnacht, November 11-- or November 9, 1938, that a number of SS-men painted swastikas and the star of David on Jewish stores, especially on the street, the Kaiser Allee, where I lived.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- well, I was out, not during the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
